<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
<expan>lantricht<ex>er</ex></expan>, uns ist von
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan> lieber <expan>b<ex>urgers</ex></expan>
                        und <expan>ratgesell<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Erhart Schurstabs
                                <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> fürbracht
                            <expan>word<ex>en</ex></expan>, wir im etliche seine gut auf das
                                <expan>lantger<ex>icht</ex></expan> gen Sulczbach
                                <expan>gelade<ex>n</ex></expan> sein <expan>word<ex>en</ex></expan>,
                        darumb er an dem nehsten <expan>lantger<ex>icht</ex></expan>
<expan>antwurte<ex>n</ex></expan> sölt, als <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> wol <expan>wissenl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
                        sey; tun wir ewch zu <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz
                                <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan> Schurstab auf disz zeit niht anheim
                        und in <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>botsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> von rats <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        awszen ist. <expan>Daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
<expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> wir ewr <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<add>mit fleiss</add>, daz ir <expan>ders<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>ladu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> umb <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>will<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ein<ex>en</ex></expan> aufslag <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und
                        anczusteen <expan>bestell<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wellet
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> und <expan>seine<ex>n</ex></expan> guten
                                <expan>unschedlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> uncz das lantgericht
                                <expan>am<ex>m</ex></expan> nehsten zu Lawff sein wurdet und uns des
                        niht verczeyhet als etc. Das <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etc. Et et
                                <expan>respo<ex>n</ex>su<ex>m</ex></expan>.
                            <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>ip<ex>s</ex>a</expan> die <expan>e<ex>pi</ex>ph<ex>an</ex>ia</expan>
<expan>d<ex>omi</ex>ni</expan>.</ab>
